						               													<description>Definition: &amp;quot;Burgeon - Begin to grow or increase rapidly&amp;quot;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Burgeon is a solo territory control game where you plant flowers and kill weeds.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game starts on a 10x10 grid with three weeds randomly planted on the board and a weather token revealed above the board. Then the player draws three cards and uses two of them to plant flowers on the board that can kill the weeds. Careful where you plant the flowers however, some will kill your plants!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each round the planted flowers and weeds grow, flourishing and spreading across the board depending on the weather. After 10 rounds, the game ends and points are scored to see if you win! The more flowers you have, the better your garden is and you gain more points. But if you have too many weeds, you'll get minus points and your garden will die.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
